title: How Nvidia and AMD could make Windows laptops feel like MacBooks
description: In an unexpected twist, it turns out that Nvidia and AMD may be developing ARM-based CPUs. Does Apple need to worry, and what about Intel?

title: Autonomous delivery robots at center of bomb scare ‘prank’
description: A bomb threat involving wheel-based delivery robots at an Oregon State University campus turned out to be a prank following the reported arrest of a suspect.
